title: Town Tamer [1965 - USA] (Dana Andrews) western
description:
Town Tamer (1965 - USA)

Action / Romance / Western

starring . . . . Dana Andrews, Terry Moore, Pat O'Brien, Lon Chaney
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0059824/


Tom Rosser is a town-taming gunman-for-hire. Only in the last town he tamed - Broken Lance, Kansas - Riley Condor put a $2,000 price tag on his head. Lee Ring tried to collect, only his bullet hit Rosser's wife, killing her. Now Rosser has followed Condor and Ring to the town of Great Plains, Texas. He's been hired by a railroad tycoon named James Fell to rid the town of it's evil element. But this time he doesn't have a star on his vest or the law on his side.
